data.meta_description:
2 likes, 0 comments - 9x16tv on April 18, 2024: "Happy 71st Birthday, Rick Moranis! 🎉

RICK MORANIS: 🎭
BIRTHDAY: April 18, 1953
BIRTH SIGN: ♈️
BIRTHPLACE: Toronto, 🇨🇦

Today, we celebrate the man who brought laughter to our lives in countless ways. From the quirky scientist in “Honey, I Shrunk the Kids” to the lovable Louis Tully in “Ghostbusters,” Rick Moranis has been a comedic force to be reckoned with.

So, on this special day, we raise our glasses to you, Rick Moranis. Thank you for the joy you’ve brought into our lives, and may your 71st year be filled with as many laughs and smiles as you’ve given us. 🥂

Happy Birthday, Rick! 🎂

#OTD
#e411news".
